      "span_text": "On the other hand, Farías-Campomanes et al. [CITATION_1] evaluated the economic feasibility of large-scale operations of supercritical fluid extraction (supercritical CO 2 containing 10% ethanol (w/w) at 313°K and 20-35 MPa) for the recovery of phenolics using grape bagasse."
    }
